Version 1 of XML Output Toggling by Textfyre begins here.

Use authorial modesty;

XML-output-flag is a truth state which varies.

Part 1A (for use with FyreVM Support by Textfyre)

XML-output-flag is true.

To decide whether XML is in use:
	if XML-output-flag is true:
		decide on whether or not FyreVM is present;
	decide no;

Part 1B (for use without FyreVM Support by Textfyre)

XML-output-flag is false.

To decide whether XML is in use:
	decide on whether or not XML-output-flag is true;

XML Output Toggling ends here.
